00:03:03,153 --> 00:03:09,707
and in Sahaja yoga we get many powers

18
00:03:10,609 --> 00:03:15,064
simultaneously, we get balance.

19
00:03:18,582 --> 00:03:21,151
We love others.

20
00:03:22,998 --> 00:03:27,735
With love and with the help of the power of Love

21
00:03:27,838 --> 00:03:32,956
we get busy in our work and go on doing our work.

22
00:03:33,395 --> 00:03:37,080
In this way, Shree Hanumanji

23
00:03:37,351 --> 00:03:39,759
was very powerful.

24
00:03:39,963 --> 00:03:42,389
He had Divine powers

25
00:03:42,495 --> 00:03:46,121
He had NAVADHA (Special) powers.

26
00:03:46,915 --> 00:03:49,673
which are called GARIMA, LAGHUMA.

27
00:03:49,698 --> 00:03:52,298
He could become as big as He wanted to be

28
00:03:52,323 --> 00:03:54,637
or as minute as He wanted to be

29
00:03:54,725 --> 00:03:58,799
and as small as an atom.

30
00:04:00,026 --> 00:04:03,430
All these powers

31
00:04:04,263 --> 00:04:06,868
He got through His devotion.

32
00:04:07,601 --> 00:04:10,897
It means that devotion and power

33
00:04:10,954 --> 00:04:13,404
are both the same.

34
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:17,138
He who has power

35
00:04:17,163 --> 00:04:21,312
and doesn't have devotion, becomes a Rakshasa (Demon).

36
00:04:22,235 --> 00:04:24,734
And He who has devotion

37
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:28,481
but doesn't have power, becomes mad.

38
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:34,196
Between both these, he who is in the central path

39
00:04:38,883 --> 00:04:46,948
attains this state which you may call power, or devotion.

40
00:04:47,047 --> 00:04:51,436
Each part of his body is made of that.

41
00:04:53,888 --> 00:05:00,888
Because of His this special feature today we worship Bajrang Bali

42
