there is no need to do anything.

201
00:19:14,785 --> 00:19:17,066
You can set them right only with the help of bandhans.

202
00:19:19,667 --> 00:19:23,366
The powers that you have received inside your being

203
00:19:23,502 --> 00:19:26,676
it should be used for this very purpose

204
00:19:26,917 --> 00:19:33,415
so that the evil will be destroyed.

205
00:19:34,929 --> 00:19:37,935
But in your power there is no sword

206
00:19:38,230 --> 00:19:41,072
or mace in your hand like Hanumanji.

