00:20:01,367 --> 00:20:05,069
you may or may not pick a mace in your hand.

211
00:20:05,549 --> 00:20:09,812
In this way you yourself are safe by default

212
00:20:10,036 --> 00:20:12,601
your safety is  guaranteed

