00:20:12,626 --> 00:20:29,058
 but along with that your other sahaja yogis too are safe.

214
00:20:30,198 --> 00:20:34,997
Now in this Shri Bajrangbali has a great role to play.

215
00:20:35,022 --> 00:20:36,553
You don't know

216
00:20:36,578 --> 00:20:40,382
that he is standing in front of you as well as at your back.

217
00:20:45,628 --> 00:20:49,044
His nature is just like children

218
00:20:50,208 --> 00:20:56,385
Too pure and too simple

