00:21:03,881 --> 00:21:07,425
and all types of virtues He knows.

221
00:21:08,891 --> 00:21:13,262
It means that along with His power

222
00:21:13,287 --> 00:21:23,103
 He has a lot of absolute discretion- very wise.

223
